        "created_at": "2020-02-09T17:30:23.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-post=\"4\" data-topic=\"158101\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>I just bought a 17 Cathiard bourgogne - will that be good to drink now or should I bury it for a decade?</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>I don\u2019t know much about the vintage but it should drink really well unless they\u2019ve changed their winemaking style has changed. Can also cellar it for apparently 15 plus years!</p>\n<p>Frenchie - agree, they only had a couple bottles but I\u2019d buy a case.</p>",
